them to the filesystem of the image at the path <code>&lt;dest&gt;</code>. Files and directories
can be copied from the build context, a remote URL, or a Git repository.</p><p>The <code>ADD</code> and <code>COPY</code> instructions are functionally similar, but serve slightly different purposes.
