<a class="link" href="https://golang.org/pkg/path/filepath#Match" rel="noopener">filepath.Match<span class="pl-1 icon-svg icon-sm"><svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 -960 960 960"><path d="M180-120q-24 0-42-18t-18-42v-6e2q0-24 18-42t42-18h249q12.75.0 21.38 8.68 8.62 8.67 8.62 21.5.0 12.82-8.62 21.32-8.63 8.5-21.38 8.5H180v6e2h6e2v-249q0-12.75 8.68-21.38 8.67-8.62 21.5-8.62 12.82.0 21.32 8.62 8.5 8.63 8.5 21.38v249q0 24-18 42t-42 18H180zm6e2-617L403-360q-9 9-21 8.5t-21-9.5-9-21 9-21l377-377H549q-12.75.0-21.37-8.68-8.63-8.67-8.63-21.5.0-12.82 8.63-21.32 8.62-8.5 21.37-8.5h261q12.75.0 21.38 8.62Q840-822.75 840-810v261q0 12.75-8.68 21.37-8.67 8.63-21.5 8.63-12.82.0-21.32-8.63-8.5-8.62-8.5-21.37v-188z"></path></svg></span></a> rules.</p><p>For example, to add all files and directories in the root of the build context
